narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: This is essentially senior essay part 1. It can be awesome or not-so-awesome depending on your adviser.
DO IT! If you've got a burning research question, this is the way to answer it. Plenty of resources, plenty of eager professors.

Do it if you have a lot of data from research over the summer, if you feel you haven't completely explored your topic yet, if you need to do more literature review, or if you simply feel that your senior essay is too big a project for one semester. It's very helpful!
Yes, I would recommend this course but only if you have a clear sense of what your project is and how you will complete it.
